properties.areaDesc: Coastal Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos California out to 10 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 8 at 2:24AM PST until January 9 at 3:00PM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt expected.

* WHERE...Coastal Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos
California out to 10 nm.

* WHEN...From 3 AM to 3 PM PST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 AM TO 3 PM PST THURSDAY
